cyto_data %>% 
  filter(prior.radiation %in% c(0,1)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = TNC.dose, y = CD3.dose, color = sex))+
  geom_point() +
  facet_grid(.~prior.radiation)+
  geom_smooth(method= "lm", se =F)+
  ggtitle("Dosage by Radation Exposure")+
  ylab("CD3 Dose") +xlab("TNC Dose")+
  theme_bw()
